---
title: Fillet Steak & Creamy Black Garlic Sauce with Zesty Chilli Fries & Garlic Butter Greens
description: There’s something eternally comforting about the aroma of a creamy black garlic sauce. Completely mouth-watering to say the
least. Drizzle it over tender premium fillet steak with a side of nutty greens and zesty chilli-baked fries, it’s time for pub-style steak and chips to move over; there’s a new and completely luxe contender in town.
